title: Microsoft Windows 7 AIO-SP1 (x64 & x86) [All in One]
description:
Microsoft Windows 7 All in One x64 & x86 (from OEM)

Modified installation DVD for Windows 7, installation options include:
Starter (x86 only)
Home Basic (x64/x86)
Home Premium (x64/x86)
Professional (x64/x86)
Ultimate (x64/x86)

Created from SP1 WIMs from previous uploads.
Be sure to  choose the proper choice during install!
As usual, must provide your own key or replacement.

All install options (minus Enterprise) available on one 4.7Gb DVD or 8Gb USB.
